{"tid":299482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"撞返以前俾過帽佢戴既前度 想一齊返 點做好","createTime":"2017-06-27T06:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T09:56:27.000Z","uid":84102,"like":5,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cacabe7e7ab45951e385d80ea918b555ee9954b7","tid":299482,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前細個唔識諗 前男友對我好好 但因為嫌佢肥 愈來愈肥 所以果陣係skout識左個男仔 佢係消防員黎 感覺好有安全感.. 好快就發生左關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後來好快俾前度知道左 但佢喊完之後話叫我唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我果陣唔識珍惜 一路拖住兩邊 戴帽佢戴，後來仲講左好多好難聽既說話同前度講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢喊到跪左係條街度 我都無理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我又斷斷續續又同幾個男仔一齊，但後來發覺 無一個男仔好似佢對我咁好，昨晚係柯士甸站見到一張好熟悉既面孔 行近啲睇原來係前度黎，佢成個人變晒 練到好fit 鋼條身形，靚仔左好多。以前戴開Casio膠錶 而家轉左rolex地通拿. 好後悔 點知可以同返佢一齊 再續前緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483d633abe2a998dee6fa5168e62c65e2c61a2a0","tid":299482,"uid":12360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"起左你底先"},{"pid":"fc1dd722dcb42bb1af82ba09a1f6583b61edde3e","tid":299482,"uid":19393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"7579e13cec25f8caa2c6833d43ba355404659a90","tid":299482,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起左你底先</blockquote><br />\n借人acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a872b34cacd2222e43731740a408bc41c1be4989","tid":299482,"uid":4596,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"自己攞嚟,俾過帽人地戴仲想同返人哋喺埋一齊.<br />\n人哋肥你就嫌棄人,就算咁好彩佢要返你,因咩事佢第時肥咗你又再比帽佢戴"},{"pid":"7274a53e2e632bee3a931af36cadbb684ee71899","tid":299482,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"